casebody.data: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Kevin PURCELL. No. D-2846. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 2, 2015. Kevin Purcell, of Rocky River, Ohio, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
